‚Ä¢ Create three Roles named: DevOps-User, Test-User and Admin.

After Creating a Role, Attach this Role to EC2 Instance.
1] go in EC2 dashboard.
2] select instance and click on Actions.
3]inside Actions Tab, click on security / Modify IAM ROLE
4]Inside Modify IAM Role, select Iam role and Click on Save Button.
